{
  "stem": "8233.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were-- we were-- at first, we were taken to work, to-- outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We would take-- we would take stones from one place and put it another one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then we would-- the following day, we would do-- take them and put them back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was-- just to make us tired and nothing constructive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day-- we were wearing pants, all pants, with a khaki top, and-- which has a cross on the back from paint-- a cross in the back.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we had kerchiefs, some kind of kerchief that everybody weared because we were--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we had wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was June.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1943.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] One day-- I always had a full face and looked healthy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I would always be the first one when they counted us to go to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day, we were not sent to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would make selections.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know for what-- we didn't know for what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then we learned that this was for some people that didn't-- I don't-- didn't like, or whatever, they would send to gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My younger sister got sick one day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was very hot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was August already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know if it was meningitis or what.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She got sick, and she didn't talk anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We took her to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, from there, they took her to a-- another camp, which was adjacent to our camp and to, like, a hospital.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They called it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She was very pretty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SOBBING] I had a friend that I found when we marched to work that would-- this was three months later, I think-- that would send us little packages through somebody.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he said that he will send something.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
